<section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28 px-6 lg:px-10">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 lg:gap-20 items-center">

			<!-- Left: Text content -->
			<div class="flex flex-col">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-5">
					<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#0C6B95] shrink-0"></span>
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-500 tracking-widest uppercase">Our Story</span>
				</div>

				<!-- Pull quote -->
				<blockquote class="border-l-4 border-[#0C6B95] pl-5 mb-8">
					<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl italic font-medium text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
						"If I could give you a gift, I would like to be able to give you what my eyes have seen."
					</p>
				</blockquote>

				<p class="text-neutral-500 text-base leading-relaxed mb-5">
					Opawey was born from the desire to share what we consider a daily privilege: the opportunity to witness the timeless beauty, rich history, and cultural magnificence of Greece. With this inspiration, we have created a bespoke service that invites others to discover these wonders in a manner that is not only elegant and comfortable, but truly unforgettable.
				</p>
				<p class="text-neutral-500 text-base leading-relaxed mb-5">
					We are a recently established family-owned business, with a shared vision: to offer high-end transportation services in Greece, focused on excellence and complete customer satisfaction. Though young as a company, we have achieved solid growth — driven by the trust our clients place in us and by our unwavering commitment to quality.
				</p>
				<p class="text-neutral-500 text-base leading-relaxed">
					We specialize in welcoming our clients upon arrival — whether at the airport or the port — and providing a smooth and elegant transfer to their hotel or any destination of their choice. We also offer personalized tours in Athens and throughout mainland Greece, designed for those who wish to explore in depth, with style and attention to detail.
				</p>

				<!-- This combination reflects -->
				<div class="mt-8 bg-[#F5F6F8] rounded-2xl p-6">
					<p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed italic">
						This combination reflects our purpose: to provide exceptional travel experiences, with the perfect balance of <span class="text-[#0C6B95] font-semibold">elegance</span>, <span class="text-[#0C6B95] font-semibold">warmth</span>, and <span class="text-neutral-800 font-semibold">professionalism</span>.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Right: Image -->
			<div class="relative">
				<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl aspect-[3/4] lg:aspect-auto lg:h-[580px]">
					<img
						src="https://picsum.photos/seed/opaway-story/800/1000"
						alt="Opawey story"
						class="w-full h-full object-cover"
					/>
				</div>
				<!-- Floating accent card -->
				<div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-[#0C6B95] text-white rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-xl max-w-[200px]">
					<p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">100%</p>
					<p class="text-sm text-white/80">Family-owned &amp; operated with passion</p>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>
